b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":3208,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"A Platinum Showcase Is Coming Soon! Shadow-Attuned 5\\u2605 Adventurer Guaranteed!","message":"<div>A Platinum Showcase starts on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1655445600\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a shadow-attuned 5\\u2605 adventurer is guaranteed to appear.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(226, 80, 65);\\">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include adventurers and dragons that are attuned to elements other than shadow.<\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>During the period, players are limited to doing the Platinum Showcase summon two times, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1655445600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1656482399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at some of the shadow-attuned 5\\u2605 adventurers eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5\\u2605 summon below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c829f34cdead347326a7fe2c1aafb424.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d54775020f2b8c24e8e1d445b58d2ad2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>752<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>506<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>2,498<\/span>\\n                <\/div><div class=\\"available-mode\\">\\n                        <div class=\\"txt\\"><span>Available Modes<\/span><\/div>\\n                        <div class=\\"icon\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/4805e47916f093eb2b9049cff29e9eb72.png\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/0ea47b25dd52e83055f02a3ca4d545522.png\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c10d099648b4bc58a4f2bde4fe0dfd752.png\\"><\/div><\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Adventurer Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The Shadowwyrm Zodiark in human form. In order<br>to reexamine love, he decided to observe human<br>activity more closely than before. But while his<br>appearance has changed, his unconditional love<br>has not, and he happily accepts any and all<br>people just as they are.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/463fc5ea424ca929ee125304b38e1bd72.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Hatecluster<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Grants the user three stacks of the \\"Malevolent<br>Rush\\" effect. Malevolent Rush grants the user<br>a third attack in their standard attack combo.<br>This attack consumes one stack of Malevolent<br>Rush, dispels one enemy buff, and, if dealt from<br>directly next to foes, applies \\"Spite.\\" Spite has<br>five levels.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Skill Energy Required: 4,329<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbMalevolent Rush<br>\\u3000\\u3000Stacks up to 3 times<br>\\u30fbSpite Lv. 1<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u30fbSpite Lv. 2<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u30fbSpite Lv. 3<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u30fbSpite Lv. 4<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbSpite Lv. 5<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 20 seconds<\/div><\/dd><dt class=\\"skill-cost-wrap\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a3661c9bf88bcc1418c169b6451357fb2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Death\'s Torrent<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"skill-cost\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Shareable<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"txt-num\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>4<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies and<br>inflicts shadowblight. If this attack hits an enemy<br>that has the \\"Spite\\" effect, it will deal bonus damage<br>based on the effect\'s level. This bonus damage<br>ignores the enemy\'s defense.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,500 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Bonus Damage (Spite Lv. 1): 300 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Bonus Damage (Spite Lv. 2): 600 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Bonus Damage (Spite Lv. 3): 900 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Bonus Damage (Spite Lv. 4): 1,200 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Bonus Damage (Spite Lv. 5): 1,500 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 9,072<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 7,348<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbShadowblight<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 31<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/85285afa2a77c2880c1c006d8d0d214c2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Gauge Accelerator +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSpeeds the rate the mode gauge decreases<br>by 20%. Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/350933fc3518d44a2f1ed162f7e191052.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Shadow) Team Strength Amp = Blindness Res +100%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Shadow:<br>reduces their susceptibility to blindness by 100%<br>when they have a team strength amp.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2556d0d8a3f335b515df8014f55973332.png\\"><\/span><span>Shadowwyrm\'s Nature II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to curses by 100%<br>and increases damage to enemies with Spite<br>by 15%.<br><br>When shapeshifting for the first time,<br>the user will transform into Zodiark regardless<br>of what dragon they are equipped with.<br>The second time onwards, they will transform<br>into High Zodiark instead.<br><br>Also, using the user\'s first or second skills will<br>grant them a strength amp with a maximum team<br>amp level of one.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f1b1dac8108a7960100a7a9673e66f772.png\\"><\/span><span>Paralysis Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to paralysis by 100%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/3c1105a9ca11c4e91051d5218bc3f2802.png\\"><\/span><span>Spectral Counter II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>When the user takes damage, fills 10% of<br>their dragon gauge and, if they have already<br>shapeshifted at least once, creates a<br>Spectral Flame where they took damage.<br>This Spectral Flame will detonate after three<br>seconds, dealing damage to surrounding<br>enemies and applying \\"Spite\\" to them.<br>After activating, these effects will not activate<br>again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/44a47dd58e6e1bbf5d907211370f29b5.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d54775020f2b8c24e8e1d445b58d2ad2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>752<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>506<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n            <div class=\\"lower-area\\">\\n                <div class=\\"total\\">\\n                    <span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n                    <span>2,498<\/span>\\n                <\/div><div class=\\"available-mode\\">\\n                        <div class=\\"txt\\"><span>Available Modes<\/span><\/div>\\n                        <div class=\\"icon\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/6312b216795ce6aa08c57851351eeb1b2.png\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d45c68ecb3b1d88cba2136c949f214772.png\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/c10d099648b4bc58a4f2bde4fe0dfd752.png\\"><\/div><\/div>\\n            <\/div>\\n        <\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Adventurer Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The Flamewyrm hits the beach with a devilishly<br>daring look to overshadow the summer sun.<br>Striking a pose with one of Chelle\'s signature<br>manacasters, she\'s aiming for her darling\'s heart!<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/3cc7e63555e75a6121c412637b8b12272.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Twilit Memory<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>reduces their defense, inflicts shadowblight,<br>and partially fills the user\'s dragondrive gauge<br>if the attack connects.<br><br>During dragondrive:<br>consumes some of the user\'s dragondrive gauge,<br>deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>reduces their defense, inflicts shadowblight,<br>then fills 100% of this skill\'s skill gauge after use.<br>Also, powers up the user\'s standard attacks.<br>This standard attack buff will be lost automatically<br>when the effect\'s remaining time is depleted<br>or when dragondrive is ended.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 513 \\u00d7 2 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 3,950<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDefense -5%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbShadowblight<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 41<br>Dragondrive Energy Gained: 300<br><br><color=#00008B>During Dragondrive:<\/color><br>Damage: 624 \\u00d7 2 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 3,950<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbDefense -5%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbEnhanced Standard Attacks<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Does not stack<br>\\u30fbShadowblight<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 21 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 41<br>Dragondrive Energy Consumed: 850<\/div><\/dd><dt\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/7bd001c2146691a592e7e2b4a13d5ca62.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>A Midsummer Night\'s Blast<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies in a line,<br>and grants the user a strength amp.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,767 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 9,855<br>Amps:<br>\\u30fbStrength Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 3)<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/85285afa2a77c2880c1c006d8d0d214c2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Gauge Accelerator +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSpeeds the rate the mode gauge decreases<br>by 20%. Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/af68964937fa01084c3d0747e6c77dda2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Shadow) Dragon Haste +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Shadow: <br>increases their dragon gauge fill rate by 20%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/bb78ae882a78ef4449c1181d5399204b2.png\\"><\/span><span>Summer Sparks II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Grants the user a dragondrive gauge, and changes<br>the shapeshift button into a dragondrive button.<br>Tapping this button activates their dragondrive.<br><br>Dragondrive grants the following effects:<br>\\u30fbThe user\'s standard attacks are changed and<br>fill the user\'s dragondrive gauge if they connect.<br>\\u30fbThe user\'s strength is increased by 25%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f1b1dac8108a7960100a7a9673e66f772.png\\"><\/span><span>Paralysis Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to paralysis by 100%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/24dc1983d110ed627df93dd3e6322d962.png\\"><\/span><span>Skill Prep +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div>\\u30fbSome skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.<\/div><div>\\u30fbAdventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about the Platinum Showcase, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select the Platinum Showcase and check the Appearance Rates section and the Details tab of the Showcase Info section.<\/div><div>2. Wyrmsigils cannot be earned from summoning on a Platinum Showcase.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1655359200,"prev_article_id":"3084","next_article_id":"3114","image_path":"","update_time":1648806271}}}'